\begin_inset space ~
\end_inset

Avatar.
 Its mandatory option is the name.
 In your case, name it 
\series bold
Oleg
\series default
.
 Add behind the name of the avatar your name as author by writing 
\series bold
author={Oleg Testman}
\series default
.
\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset

